{"name":"Minerva McGonagall","nameCn":"米勒娃·麦格","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/fc/50/86040_crt_jjE3R.jpg","info":"<li><span>简体中文名: </span>米勒娃·麦格</li><li><span>性别: </span>女</li><li><span>生日: </span>1935年10月4日</li><li><span>引用来源: </span>https://harrypotter.fandom.com/zh/wiki/</li>","detail":"米勒娃·麦格 (Minerva McGonagall)（生于1935年10月4日）是一个女巫，也是一个登记在册的阿尼马格斯。她于1947年至1954年间曾在霍格沃茨魔法学校就读，并被分入格兰芬多学院。毕业后，她在魔法部工作了两年，后来又重新回到霍格沃茨。她在学校是一个变形学教授，后来成为格兰芬多学院院长和学校副校长。<br /><br />麦格还是第一次和第二次凤凰社的成员。1995年，她反对霍格沃茨高级调查官多洛雷斯·乌姆里奇在学校的所作所为。1997年至1998年间，她又暗中保护学生们不受阿莱克托和阿米库斯·卡罗的伤害。她参加了天文塔大战和霍格沃茨大战，并在霍格沃茨大战中带领师生进行了顽强的抵抗。<br /><br />第二次巫师战争结束后，她被正式任命为霍格沃茨校长。在继续工作了一段时间之后，她从校长的位置上退休。","jobs":[{"href":"/subject/213026","name":"Fantastic Beasts: The Crimes of Grindelwald","nameCn":"神奇动物在哪里：格林德沃之罪","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/9f/49/213026_cWZZS.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"Fiona Glascott","castHref":"/person/39658","castTag":"CV","castCover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/3a/52/39658_prsn_kRFrp.jpg"},{"href":"/subject/293028","name":"Lego Harry Potter: Years 5–7","nameCn":"乐高哈利波特：第 5-7 年","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/18/7b/293028_dLUUJ.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":""},{"href":"/subject/7192","name":"LEGO Harry Potter: Years 1-4","nameCn":"乐高：哈利波特","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/73/ef/7192_zV5LQ.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":""},{"href":"/subject/194039","name":"Harry Potter and the Cursed Child","nameCn":"哈利·波特与被诅咒的孩子","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/d8/85/194039_us.jpg","staff":"配角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":""},{"href":"/subject/78306","name":"Harry Potter","nameCn":"哈利·波特","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/51/5a/78306_qhf59.jpg","staff":"配角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":""},{"href":"/subject/60119","name":"Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets","nameCn":"哈利·波特与密室","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/c8/7a/60119_56prO.jpg","staff":"配角","cast":"Maggie Smith","castHref":"/pe